check_iftraffic.pl Nagios Plugin for monitoring traffic loads on interfaces
using SNMP.

This is a fork of the well-known check_iftraffic.pl plugins done by Markus
Werner, Greg Frater and Ektanoor. 

Development is done by Bernhard Schmidt <berni@birkenwald.de>. The source
code is available at GitHub 
(https://github.com/bernhardschmidt/nagios-check-iftraffic). Patches are
welcome
